vulnerability_details: Like the baiji navigating by echolocation in muddy waters,
  Chen relied on generational knowledge of river sounds and seasonal patterns to fish
  sustainably. Industrial noise from new shipping lanes and dam construction has made
  her traditional navigation methods obsolete, forcing displacement from ancestral
  fishing grounds.
